title: Modern 1 Bedroom In Pac Heights Walk To Union St. & Fillmore Shops
posting_body: ['2200 Jackson St.', 'Welcome to Pacific Heights.', "Being one of San Francisco's most prestigious neighborhoods, you're moments away from the shops, restaurants, and entertainment on Fillmore and Union Street.", 'Remodeled gorgeous 1 bedroom & 1 bath is waiting for you!', '- 2nd Floor With Patio', '- Remodel Kitchen & Bathroom', '- Caesarstone Counter Tops', '- Stainless Steel Appliances W/Dishwasher & Microwave', '- Plank Flooring', '- Parking Available', '- Laundry On-Site', '- Water, Sewer & Garbage Included', '- Minutes from Public Transportation and Shops', '- Walkscore rating is 93', '- Walk to Lafayette Park, Alta Plaza Park, Fillmore & Union St. shops', '- Muni lines 3, 10 & 24 nearby', 'Please copy and paste the link to view our 3D tour:  <URL>', "Don't miss this opportunity.", 'Call today to schedule a tour of your new home at', 'show contact info', 'Trinity specializes in renting furnished and unfurnished apartments throughout San Francisco.', 'For more information please visit us online at <URL>', '* No pets allowed.', '* Features may not be available in all units.', 'This unit is a rental unit subject to the San Francisco Rent Ordinance, which limits evictions without just cause, and which states that any waiver by a tenant of their rights under the Rent Ordinance is void as contrary to public policy.', 'TMS']
